.START 

The acquisition of A.M.E. Inc. by A.M.E. Holding Co., a new concern formed by Lawrence J. Berkowitz has been completed, A.M.E. Inc said.
The merger is valued at about $61 million. 

A.M.E. provides videotape post-production services.
Mr. Berkowitz is former chairman of a payroll company for the entertainment industry. 

